      "text": [
        "559 - قَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «مَا مِنْ أَحَدٍ يَمُوتُ أَحَبَّ إِلَى إِبْلِيسَ مِنْ مَوْتِ فَقِيهٍ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.559 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"There is no one whose death is more beloved to Iblis than the death of a scholar (faqih).\""
        ]
      }
    }
